Configuration for simulated data generation

Source: R/simFunction.R
configuration_setting_generation.Rd

generate the configuration for the data

Usage

configuration_setting_generation(
  featureNum = 50,
  DataNum = c(100, 100, 100, 100),
  commonlySharedNum = 2,
  partiallySharedNum = c(2, 2, 2, 2),
  individualSharedNum = c(2, 2, 2, 2),
  noiseVariance = c(1, 1, 1, 1)
)

Arguments

featureNum

number of features

DataNum

number of data

commonlySharedNum

number of common component

partiallySharedNum

number of partial shared component

individualSharedNum

number of individual component

noiseVariance

variance of noise

Examples

configuration_setting_generation()
